QuestData.Title: Deeper into Darkness
QuestData.Description: The Skitterweb matriarch is nearby! You can put an end to the Skitterweb menace by killing her!$B$BFind the brood mother at the end of the cave in the Skittering Dark and destroy her!
QuestData.RewardText: You rescued our orcs and killed the Skitterweb matriarch? We owe you a great debt of gratitude. You've saved us all from certain execution, $n. I'm sure we can rouse these drunken idiots now.
